title: TREEHOUSE (2019) Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: I'm just here for the soufflé!
It was ok the mask looked totally spooky and I dug them! The “witches” where so in your face it was goofy so overall it was interesting
Pooka! is still the best one.

In addition to all of the connections that the cast have to writer and director James Roday, I also found it kind of fun that the British "witch" that was pointing the arrows at Peter happened to be the actor Jimmi Simpson's fiance in real life.
I've been watching this channel since castle rock. This channel is amazing. It has grown so much!!!......i actually think  treehouse was the best in the collection. 👍
description:
We take a look at Hulu's latest horror installment "Treehouse" part of their "Into the Dark" series and delve into its ending to solve some of the hidden mysteries within!
